      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions or equivalent benchmark demonstrates correct implementation of governing equations to within expected truncation error order.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations confirms second-order spatial convergence. Benchmark results are consistent with published solver verification studies for rotating machinery."
