      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) within validation uncertainty bounds across all five operating points; RH < 1 for worst-case condition.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis agrees with experimental measurements within combined simulation and experimental uncertainty (U95 = 18%) at all five operating points. Worst-case RH = 0.87, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Achieved level exceeds requirement due to comprehensive uncertainty quantification."
