      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmark comparisons for rotating blood-contacting devices. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model validated against erythrocyte lysis data. Sensitivity analysis confirms model form uncertainty within acceptable bounds for MRL 2."
    },
    {
