    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors scoped out per MRL 2 assessment plan with documented justification. The CFD model demonstrates adequate credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Worst-case relative hemolysis index (RH = 0.87) satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion within quantified uncertainty bounds. Assessment package accepted for regulatory submission.",
